    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様で～す。お仕事の調子はどうですか～？",
      "startTime": 3.1666666109,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様。仕事は……まぁいつも通りだな\nこころはどうしたんだ？",
      "startTime": 13.7666666984,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "ハード過ぎる現場の合間に顔を出してあげたんですよ～\nどうですか？　かわゆい顔を見て癒されますか～？",
      "startTime": 19.8414513667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そうだなー。こころのおかげで凄く癒されたぞー\nさーて、残りの仕事も頑張るか……",
      "startTime": 29.5000000317,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "対応が雑！　アイドルのマネージャーたるもの\nもっと言葉選びに力を入れて下さい！",
      "startTime": 36.0678744316,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんごめん、ちょうど大事なメールが届いて……\nお……こころ、一つ仕事が決まったぞ",
      "startTime": 43.3000000317,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "お仕事？　私にですか？",
      "startTime": 47.7405894993,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "この間リズノワで東京シーサイドのCMを撮影しただろ\nあの時のプロデューサーから連絡があってな",
      "startTime": 54.5333333651,
      "sfxList": []
    }
